could be leading information.

03:03.539 --> 03:06.815
This museum has a lot of photographs.

03:06.816 --> 03:10.160
So it's important that I remove them all..

03:10.161 --> 03:14.601
To avoid influencing Amy during her walk.

03:28.054 --> 03:30.754
There's a fire.

03:31.153 --> 03:33.913
Somebody help me.

03:46.576 --> 03:48.496
Okay.

03:48.623 --> 03:51.651
There's a lot of dead people here.

03:51.652 --> 03:57.052
So I'd say that this town
is pretty freaking active.

03:57.457 --> 04:00.995
As soon as I arrived, dozens
of dead people surrounded me,

04:00.996 --> 04:04.467
all wanting to share their stories.

04:04.468 --> 04:09.868
I just see a lot of dead
bodies all over the place.

04:12.166 --> 04:14.926
It's really bad.

04:28.852 --> 04:32.543
So, Debbie, what's going on here
that you needed to call us in?

04:32.544 --> 04:37.176
Well, I'm a tour guide, and we seem
to be having some unusual activity

04:37.177 --> 04:38.289
happening here.

04:38.290 --> 04:41.280
And it's getting more and more frequent.

04:41.281 --> 04:44.517
We're hearing things, we're
seeing things, object are moving,

04:44.518 --> 04:47.818
and it really scares me.

04:51.114 --> 04:53.412
What exactly is the Mackay Mansion?

04:53.413 --> 04:59.313
Well, the Mackay Mansion was where
John Mackay had his mining office.

04:59.475 --> 05:04.647
He made quite a bit of money
up here during his day.

05:04.648 --> 05:07.583
And this was where all his
businesses took place.

05:07.584 --> 05:10.177
- And now it's a museum.
- Yes.

05:10.178 --> 05:11.804
Why are you staying?

05:11.805 --> 05:13.436
I love this too much.

05:13.437 --> 05:16.503
And how often in life do you
find a job that you love to do?

05:16.504 --> 05:18.232
Are you concerned for your safety?

05:18.233 --> 05:22.873
Yeah, because I don't know who or
what it may be, what it wants, and..

05:22.874 --> 05:25.164
And it just makes you feel like it..

05:25.165 --> 05:29.245
What it wants isn't gonna be good.

05:33.019 --> 05:35.599
Wait a minute.

05:39.520 --> 05:42.435
There's a little girl..

05:42.436 --> 05:45.856
Who runs around the place.

05:47.879 --> 05:53.613
She's got long brown hair, it's
curled and put up with a bow,

05:53.614 --> 05:57.334
brown eyes, chubby little face.

05:57.931 --> 06:03.271
I want to say like 7, but,
uh, she's got problems.

06:11.190 --> 06:13.864
So, Debbie, what's going on in here?

06:13.865 --> 06:19.765
Well, a lot of people have reported seeing
the spirit of a little girl up here.

06:20.807 --> 06:22.326
So one night, some friends and I

06:22.327 --> 06:25.144
decided to come in here and
make contact with her,

06:25.145 --> 06:28.065
let her know that we know she's here.

06:28.066 --> 06:29.804
I just kind of said, "you
know, if you're here,"

06:29.805 --> 06:32.202
"can you give us some kind of sign?"

06:32.203 --> 06:36.627
And this toy box right here, the lid,
all of a sudden comes falling down.

06:36.628 --> 06:40.334
This blanket that's right
here starts going up and over

06:40.335 --> 06:42.469
this guy's shoulder, all on its own.

06:42.470 --> 06:45.940
He's sitting right in front of the toy box.

06:45.941 --> 06:46.975
I mean, this is heavy.

06:46.976 --> 06:48.054
It is.

06:48.055 --> 06:49.172
And this got pulled up?

06:49.173 --> 06:52.893
The blanket started coming out.

06:54.273 --> 06:56.471
I don't know. I think I would've been
outta here in a New York minute.

06:56.472 --> 07:00.363
I don't think I would've stuck around.

07:00.364 --> 07:03.211
The little girl's running around, laughing.

07:03.212 --> 07:04.752
"Ha ha."

07:04.753 --> 07:06.588
"Hee hee hee hee hee."

07:06.589 --> 07:09.387
She likes to jump on things.

07:09.388 --> 07:12.401
She likes to hide in things.

07:12.402 --> 07:15.582
She's a little rascal.

07:17.259 --> 07:21.279
People would get nervous from this.

07:24.801 --> 07:27.687
So do people experience her doing things?

07:27.688 --> 07:30.867
I would think that they would.

07:30.868 --> 07:36.084
If you're in bed, you might feel
her, like, crawl on the bed.

07:36.085 --> 07:38.702
She's in the wardrobe,
and you hear little..

07:38.703 --> 07:42.663
Tick.. Tick.. Tick..
Tick.. Tick..

07:43.769 --> 07:46.109
She's bad.

07:54.291 --> 07:56.845
So, Debbie, what have you
experienced down here?

07:56.846 --> 07:58.612
I was on a tour, and all of a sudden,

07:58.613 --> 08:02.474
this shadowy figure just
appeared by the gazebo.

08:02.475 --> 08:03.373
And..

08:03.374 --> 08:06.328
It had, like, these glowing eyes.

08:06.329 --> 08:10.573
It was like terror just kind of took
over my body, and I.. I couldn't move.

08:10.574 --> 08:12.209
Now have you seen him close?

08:12.210 --> 08:14.046
Yes.

08:14.047 --> 08:19.947
Every time it's been seen now, it's
coming closer and closer to the house.

08:28.124 --> 08:30.557
Oh, there's a big old guy..

08:30.558 --> 08:33.498
A pretty tall dude.

08:35.563 --> 08:41.443
Uh, you know, he likes to kinda
freak people out, you know?

08:41.457 --> 08:44.871
I'm seeing a large dead man
moving within the shadows.

08:44.872 --> 08:48.513
It feels like he's stalking me,
like he's waiting to attack,

08:48.514 --> 08:54.214
and I know I'm not the first
person he's done this to.

08:55.747 --> 08:57.951
Big guy is not so nice.

08:57.952 --> 08:59.360
Like, evil.

08:59.361 --> 09:02.907
Probably just looks like a
big, dark, scary thing.

09:02.908 --> 09:07.348
He works really hard at.. At being seen.

09:07.410 --> 09:09.363
I don't like this place.

09:09.364 --> 09:12.484
I don't like it all.

09:19.929 --> 09:23.091
There's a big old guy..

09:23.092 --> 09:27.781
Which probably just looks like a big,
dark scary thing, maybe, to most people.

09:27.782 --> 09:32.162
He likes to freak people out, you know?

09:33.243 --> 09:35.085
Debbie's told me all
about the bizarre things

09:35.086 --> 09:37.378
that she's been seeing
at the Mackay Mansion.

09:37.379 --> 09:40.893
But I can't hang the entire
case on a single eyewitness.

09:40.894 --> 09:44.535
So I'm going to meet with a woman who
allegedly had a terrifying experience

09:44.536 --> 09:48.616
while taking a tour at the mansion.

09:54.234 --> 09:56.509
So, Valerie, when did
you take the tour here?

09:56.510 --> 09:58.707
I took the tour six months ago.

09:58.708 --> 09:59.894
What happened on the tour?

09:59.895 --> 10:03.863
We started to walk, and I was
the last one in the back.

10:03.864 --> 10:09.204
All of a sudden, I hear what
sounded like footsteps.

10:12.373 --> 10:16.402
And I just happened to glance
over, and I saw this..

10:16.403 --> 10:19.187
Tall shadow.. Man.

10:19.188 --> 10:21.828
And he stopped.

10:21.939 --> 10:26.769
Turned around and looked at me with
these evil-looking, glowing eyes.

10:26.770 --> 10:29.355
Did he.. Did he say anything?
Did you hear anything?

10:29.356 --> 10:30.701
He didn't say anything.

10:30.702 --> 10:35.082
He just glared me down with these eyes.

10:36.203 --> 10:39.335
Valerie, after this thing
disappeared, what did you do?

10:39.336 --> 10:42.187
I dropped to my knees and started crying.

10:42.188 --> 10:45.444
I was very hysterical and very scared.

10:45.445 --> 10:47.138
I had nightmares.

10:47.139 --> 10:50.574
It made me wake up every hour..

10:50.575 --> 10:53.956
Every night. And I couldn't sleep.

10:53.957 --> 10:56.589
I want to face my fears,
but at the same time,

10:56.590 --> 10:59.917
I'm scared to death of
what may happen next.

10:59.918 --> 11:03.098
What he might do next.

11:07.986 --> 11:10.110
- You okay?
- Yeah.

11:10.111 --> 11:12.189
What's going on?

11:12.190 --> 11:15.430
I felt like a.. Impact.

11:15.513 --> 11:17.297
Somebody shoving, pushing.

11:17.298 --> 11:19.112
Okay.

11:19.113 --> 11:21.813
Something about..

11:21.815 --> 11:24.084
The ground.

11:24.085 --> 11:28.165
Because it absorbed a lot of death.

11:31.872 --> 11:33.672
Mm.

11:35.500 --> 11:38.980
This is really, really bad.

11:43.282 --> 11:45.420
Both Debbie and Valerie
have seen a shadow figure

11:45.421 --> 11:47.838
stalking the grounds of the Mackay Mansion.

11:47.839 --> 11:49.683
Now I'm on my way to speak
with a third witness

11:49.684 --> 11:53.824
who says he had a similar encounter.

12:00.278 --> 12:02.399
So, Tom, when did you take Debbie's tour?

12:02.400 --> 12:06.408
Uh, it was back in, uh, I
would say November of 2009.

12:06.409 --> 12:08.117
Okay, what happened on that tour?

12:08.118 --> 12:10.765
Down by the gazebo there,
I saw a shadow figure.

12:10.766 --> 12:14.538
So I kind of hung back, you know,
seeing if I could see it again.

12:14.539 --> 12:17.229
And then all of a sudden, it
felt like I was covered in lead.

12:17.230 --> 12:18.832
You know, just heavy, you know?

12:18.833 --> 12:22.133
And, um, trying to move,
and I just couldn't.

12:22.134 --> 12:24.722
At that point, I was panicking pretty good.

12:24.723 --> 12:27.288
And I said to it, you know, "let me go,"

12:27.289 --> 12:29.011
you know, "talk to me or let me go,"

12:29.012 --> 12:33.707
and it was like a.. Like a light
breeze, it just lifted off of me.

12:33.708 --> 12:37.737
So I was pretty skeptical, you
know, then, but, uh, not now.

12:37.738 --> 12:41.098
Not after that experience.

12:48.927 --> 12:50.426
Whoa. (Bleep)

