What's wrong?

12:56.526 --> 12:59.826
I don't like that room.

13:04.718 --> 13:07.389
What's wrong with the room?

13:07.390 --> 13:10.870
It's, like, very dangerous.

13:12.878 --> 13:16.139
It was, like, I walked
in, and it felt like..

13:16.140 --> 13:18.791
I got, like, pushed out.

13:18.792 --> 13:21.316
And there was like this..

13:21.317 --> 13:23.957
Wall of, like..

13:23.973 --> 13:26.660
Like a wall of darkness.

13:26.661 --> 13:31.094
And then I just felt like
I was being pushed out.

13:31.095 --> 13:33.915
And it scared me.

13:42.299 --> 13:46.297
I gotta start digging deeper
into the Mackay Mansion's past.

13:46.298 --> 13:50.350
Especially about the man
who built it, John Mackay.

13:50.351 --> 13:56.251
