to start is with a local historian.

14:01.604 --> 14:04.363
As you know, I'm investigating the
Mackay Mansion in Virginia City.

14:04.364 --> 14:05.102
Yes.

14:05.103 --> 14:07.939
What I don't know a lot about
is Virginia City itself.

14:07.940 --> 14:11.794
By 1859, we had thousands
of people coming in

14:11.795 --> 14:14.432
