14:14.433 --> 14:19.568
People from around the world were rushing
over here to make their fortunes.

14:19.569 --> 14:20.986
Mining's dangerous today.

14:20.987 --> 14:22.326
How was it then?

14:22.327 --> 14:24.243
Were there any tragedies
close to the Mackay Mansion?

