with a small daughter.

15:32.855 --> 15:34.290
So how'd she wind up with Mackay?

15:34.291 --> 15:36.604
His mining partner introduced 'em.

15:36.605 --> 15:39.209
Okay, and at some point, they must
have lived in the mansion together?

15:39.210 --> 15:43.190
Yes, and he adopted her, uh, 4-
or 5-year-old daughter that, um,

15:43.191 --> 15:44.305
had a disability.

15:44.306 --> 15:46.751
