15:53.207 --> 15:55.145
There's a little girl.

15:55.146 --> 15:58.446
The same girl as before.

15:59.010 --> 16:01.086
She's a bad girl.

16:01.087 --> 16:04.395
Like, she likes to scare people.

16:04.396 --> 16:05.883
I guess she's just playing?

16:05.884 --> 16:07.914
Uh.. Yeah.

16:07.915 --> 16:13.815
I mean, she is just playing, but
she's out of control, you know?

16:14.338 --> 16:18.358
She looks healthy, but she wasn't.

16:20.601 --> 16:23.122
So when she meets, uh, John
Mackay, he's not wealthy.

16:23.123 --> 16:26.885
But she was accustomed to, I guess, a
lifestyle of living with a Doctor.

16:26.886 --> 16:29.831
She definitely always felt
that she deserved a..

16:29.832 --> 16:31.845
