I think she does this to living
people in the house, too.

18:04.218 --> 18:07.038
She's destructive.

18:07.954 --> 18:09.564
I don't like her.

18:09.565 --> 18:12.085
She's creepy.

18:12.527 --> 18:14.858
She doesn't have a soul.

18:14.859 --> 18:17.319
She's empty.

