This whole town is connected by
600 miles of underground tunnels

18:22.284 --> 18:25.689
where thousands of miners
died horrible deaths.

18:25.690 --> 18:26.949
So I'm headed over to meet a guy

18:26.950 --> 18:30.254
who knows the mining history
in this town inside and out.

18:30.255 --> 18:34.155
There could be a connection here.

18:38.066 --> 18:41.395
So, Ron, I was talking to a local
historian, and, uh, she mentioned that

