Ground was bad or..

19:38.504 --> 19:41.264
Was worse before.

19:44.111 --> 19:46.975
It was worse. It was worse before.

19:46.976 --> 19:49.872
I just feel, like, a lot of death.

19:49.873 --> 19:54.853
And I also see a lot of
bodies on the ground.

19:56.493 --> 19:59.338
Did you know anyone who died
in these mining disasters?

19:59.339 --> 20:04.585
My great-grandfather died at
3,000-foot level in 1880..

20:04.586 --> 20:05.837
And he was 29.

20:05.838 --> 20:07.147
Can I ask how he died?

20:07.148 --> 20:12.253
Something slipped off of the cage that
hauled, uh, material up and down,

20:12.254 --> 20:15.725
and he was unfortunate enough
to be at the bottom of that.

20:15.726 --> 20:20.132
It decapitated him, and it killed a couple
of other fellas right at that time,

20:20.133 --> 20:22.036
and then another one died later.

20:22.037 --> 20:24.437
Oh, my God.

20:25.861 --> 20:29.881
One guy, he.. Had his head broken.

20:30.928 --> 20:31.693
Yuck.

20:31.694 --> 20:33.734
(Bleep)

20:34.530 --> 20:37.890
Uh, his head was cracked.

20:55.287 --> 20:58.022
There's, like, all these men.

20:58.023 --> 21:00.439
There's probably like 40 guys.

21:00.440 --> 21:03.500
They're all in pain.

21:09.141 --> 21:11.516
That's all I can get off of them.

21:11.517 --> 21:15.366
Because nobody's, uh, well enough..

21:15.367 --> 21:17.527
To talk.

21:18.464 --> 21:20.209
These men are still in their death state,

21:20.210 --> 21:24.020
which means they're reliving their
deaths over and over again.

21:24.021 --> 21:26.985
And they're in too much pain
to communicate with me.

21:26.986 --> 21:29.386
I feel bad.

21:33.740 --> 21:36.278
With so many men dying in
these underground mines,

21:36.279 --> 21:39.998
Virginia City might as well
be built on a graveyard.

21:39.999 --> 21:41.765
But my witnesses aren't seeing men.

21:41.766 --> 21:45.411
They're seeing a young
girl and a shadow figure.

21:45.412 --> 21:47.348
The girl could be Mackay's stepdaughter.

21:47.349 --> 21:51.009
But how do I I.D. a shadow?

21:51.858 --> 21:55.479
All I can do is keep finding
deaths surrounding this place..

21:55.480 --> 21:59.740
And see if Amy can make sense of it.

22:12.271 --> 22:13.761
It turns out a pretty gruesome murder

22:13.762 --> 22:17.035
took place right next to
the mansion in the 1800s.

22:17.036 --> 22:21.836
The victim..
A prostitute named Julia Bulette.

22:24.511 --> 22:27.929
This Julia Bulette
homicide's got my attention.

22:27.930 --> 22:30.506
According to maps, her body
was discovered in her home,

22:30.507 --> 22:33.407
not far from the Mackay Mansion.

22:33.408 --> 22:35.024
I'm headed over to talk to an historian

22:35.025 --> 22:37.159
who's been obsessed with
this case for years.

22:37.160 --> 22:42.320
I'm hoping she can tell
me exactly what happened.

22:55.442 --> 23:01.342
Julia Bulette was a prostitute that
was murdered in January 20, 1867.

23:02.982 --> 23:08.382
She was a very well-loved
and, uh, famous prostitute.

23:08.686 --> 23:10.472
The motive was robbery.

23:10.473 --> 23:14.197
All of her belongings, uh, were taken.

23:14.198 --> 23:16.653
Being that she was a high-end
prostitute back in those days,

23:16.654 --> 23:20.708
would she have serviced men in her
house or would she go to their home?

23:20.709 --> 23:22.988
She did service a lot of
the men in her house..

23:22.989 --> 23:24.496
Probably a lot of the miner men..

23:24.497 --> 23:30.397
But she probably serviced, uh, many
of the mine superintendents as well.

23:30.419 --> 23:33.486
I know the Mackay Mansion used to be
a boarding house for superintendents

23:33.487 --> 23:35.374
before John Mackay bought it.

23:35.375 --> 23:38.719
And given Julia Bulette's
popularity with the men in town,

23:38.720 --> 23:41.837
I have no doubt that she had her own key.

23:41.838 --> 23:45.318
Yeah, that's very possible.

23:45.944 --> 23:47.897
How old was she at the time of her death?

23:47.898 --> 23:50.298
She was 34.

23:52.441 --> 23:55.579
There was a guy around here.

23:55.580 --> 23:57.656
He wanders around the town.

23:57.657 --> 24:01.077
He wanders around in here.

24:01.767 --> 24:04.887
He was killing ladies.

24:06.636 --> 24:09.827
This one lady he killed was..

24:09.828 --> 24:11.557
30s, 40s.

24:11.558 --> 24:13.939
What do you know about the
actual physical damage to her?

24:13.940 --> 24:17.519
She was found laying on
her left side in the bed.

24:17.520 --> 24:22.019
Um, and she had two, uh, blunt
force traumas to the head.

24:22.020 --> 24:24.856
And then she had a pillow
placed over her face.

24:24.857 --> 24:26.298
Was somebody arrested in this case?

24:26.299 --> 24:29.996
Yes. There was a gentleman named
John Milleain who was arrested.

24:29.997 --> 24:31.326
Okay, was he a local?

24:31.327 --> 24:35.227
Um, no. He was a French drifter.

24:36.608 --> 24:39.118
He, like, didn't live here.

24:39.119 --> 24:41.456
Uh, or anywhere around here.

24:41.457 --> 24:43.123
He'd travel all over.

24:43.124 --> 24:45.012
He was..

24:45.013 --> 24:46.097
Like a roamer.

24:46.098 --> 24:48.618
He was crazy.

24:54.466 --> 24:55.887
Did Milleain ever go to trial?

24:55.888 --> 24:58.099
Yes. John Milleain, uh, did go to trial.

24:58.100 --> 24:59.897
The trial lasted only two days.

24:59.898 --> 25:01.447
Did he admit to it?

25:01.448 --> 25:05.111
He admitted to having been
there at her property,

25:05.112 --> 25:07.321
uh, but claimed that he was
with two other gentlemen

25:07.322 --> 25:08.770
who actually did the attack.

25:08.771 --> 25:09.662
Was he convicted?

25:09.663 --> 25:13.383
Yes, he was sentenced to hang.

25:14.738 --> 25:16.150
It was quite the spectacle.

25:16.151 --> 25:19.050
I would say the majority
of the town turned out.

25:19.051 --> 25:22.725
There were two days in Virginia City's
history that the bars were closed.

25:22.726 --> 25:24.316
One was the day of her funeral

25:24.317 --> 25:29.777
and the other was the day
that her killer was hanged.

25:36.150 --> 25:38.305
I'm seeing a hanging around here.

25:38.306 --> 25:39.056
Okay.

25:39.057 --> 25:42.007
There's some wacko guy hanging..

25:42.008 --> 25:44.438
Swinging in the breeze.

25:44.439 --> 25:45.904
Swinging in the breeze.

25:45.905 --> 25:47.500
What's he hanging from?

25:47.501 --> 25:49.612
A tree, I think.

25:49.613 --> 25:51.317
I don't know.

25:51.318 --> 25:55.638
It may be symbolic. It's psychic, so..

25:55.715 --> 25:58.662
Images of a hanging are
flashing through my mind.

25:58.663 --> 26:00.514
I'm seeing a picture of what happened here,

26:00.515 --> 26:04.346
and this execution had
everyone's attention.

26:04.347 --> 26:07.587
Something about justice..

26:08.014 --> 26:12.154
Like, I just see the word "justice."

26:26.313 --> 26:29.198
I came across a lot of dead
people during my walk,

26:29.199 --> 26:33.137
but the nasty woman with the
icy-cold touch is standing over me,

26:33.138 --> 26:38.080
and she's demanding that I sketch
her the way she sees herself.

26:38.081 --> 26:40.136
She would be..

26:40.137 --> 26:43.257
Mid 30s to early 40s.

26:47.315 --> 26:50.615
What shape was her face?

26:52.055 --> 26:54.126
Her face is round.

26:54.127 --> 26:56.422
She has very thin lips.

26:56.423 --> 27:01.158
Was the..
Lower lip as thin as the upper lip?

27:01.159 --> 27:06.019
It's a little bit larger
than the upper lip.

27:07.546 --> 27:10.928
She is really angry, and she..

27:10.929 --> 27:14.058
Wants to look a certain way.

27:14.059 --> 27:16.186
Her hair is dark.

27:16.187 --> 27:19.067
Eyelashes are dark.

27:22.343 --> 27:25.403
Is this who you saw?

27:25.867 --> 27:27.727
Yes.

27:51.776 --> 27:54.903
Over the last several days, Amy
and I have been conducting

27:54.904 --> 27:57.854
completely separate investigations.

27:57.855 --> 28:03.315
Tonight will be the first
time we reveal our findings.

28:03.693 --> 28:06.114
Debbie is the tour guide here.

28:06.115 --> 28:09.426
Uh, she loves this job and she
doesn't want to leave it.

28:09.427 --> 28:13.579
But she's having some experiences
that has her a little frightened.

28:13.580 --> 28:16.662
Valerie, uh, was actually..
Took a tour here,

28:16.663 --> 28:19.490
and during the tour, she was traumatized

28:19.491 --> 28:22.010
to the point where she
didn't sleep for two weeks.

28:22.011 --> 28:24.222
She had nightmares.

28:24.223 --> 28:25.790
She needs answers.

28:25.791 --> 28:28.751
She wants to face her fears and
find out what's going on here,

28:28.752 --> 28:31.345
so that's why they called us in.

28:31.346 --> 28:37.246
So with that being said, maybe Amy
could tell us about her walk.

28:42.261 --> 28:47.598
I saw this crazy guy who was
killing a lot of women.

28:47.599 --> 28:51.592
You know, he did all this..
Strangled these women, mutilated them.

28:51.593 --> 28:54.086
It wasn't just one.. One lady.

28:54.087 --> 28:56.300
He makes me feel sick.

28:56.301 --> 28:59.541
He was, like, a roamer.

28:59.818 --> 29:04.258
He was killing ladies
and he was crazy.

29:10.673 --> 29:14.071
You know, Amy, that sounds a lot
like the Julia Bulette case.

29:14.072 --> 29:17.397
Before John Mackay had lived here, this
was the home for the superintendents.

29:17.398 --> 29:19.567
Most of the time, they didn't
have their wives with them.

29:19.568 --> 29:22.758
So the chances of Julia
Bulette, who was a prostitute

29:22.759 --> 29:24.375
literally a couple of blocks from here,

29:24.376 --> 29:27.127
servicing the men in this
house is pretty good.

29:27.128 --> 29:30.488
Here's a picture of her.

29:30.733 --> 29:35.227
She was 34 when she was murdered,
literally a couple of blocks from here,

29:35.228 --> 29:37.078
uh, by a drifter.

29:37.079 --> 29:37.971
Wow.

29:37.972 --> 29:40.892
She was bludgeoned about the head,

29:40.893 --> 29:43.308
uh, blunt force trauma, and
she was strangled to death.

29:43.309 --> 29:44.335
And when they found her, they had..

29:44.336 --> 29:45.982
There was a pillow over her face also.

29:45.983 --> 29:49.402
So this guy John Milleain, who I have
a photo of, when he murdered her,

29:49.403 --> 29:53.359
I guess he wanted to
make sure she was dead.

29:53.360 --> 29:57.560
It wasn't the first time he did it.

29:58.455 --> 30:00.992
I also saw a hanging.

30:00.993 --> 30:02.853
Hmm.

30:03.617 --> 30:06.272
Hanging from a tree, like swaying.

30:06.273 --> 30:10.353
I did see the.. The word "justice."

30:10.557 --> 30:12.160
That makes sense.

30:12.161 --> 30:13.867
Totally makes sense.

30:13.868 --> 30:16.761
He was convicted in two days of her murder.

30:16.762 --> 30:21.322
But it took a year
before he was hanged.

30:25.095 --> 30:29.987
What I saw was residual energy, like a
piece of a movie replaying over and over.

30:29.988 --> 30:34.035
I saw a man killing women, but I
couldn't make out his features.

30:34.036 --> 30:36.116
I also saw a hanging.

30:36.117 --> 30:39.305
So now this all makes sense.

30:39.306 --> 30:40.328
What else did you see?

30:40.329 --> 30:42.476
This woman..

30:42.477 --> 30:44.577
Who was

30:44.585 --> 30:46.962
extremely angry.

30:46.963 --> 30:49.992
And she was yelling at her husband.

30:49.993 --> 30:53.100
Um, she apparently had..

30:53.101 --> 30:57.343
Had a much better lifestyle
before she moved here.

30:57.344 --> 30:58.737
And went with him.

30:58.738 --> 31:03.298
And she was missing that upscale lifestyle.

31:03.524 --> 31:06.017
And she was standing by me..

31:06.018 --> 31:10.482
And she put her arm on my arm,
and it was, like, ice cold.

31:10.483 --> 31:12.343
Ice.

31:14.132 --> 31:17.045
She's, like, destructive. Um..

31:17.046 --> 31:19.735
I don't like her.

31:19.736 --> 31:20.914
She's right here.

31:20.915 --> 31:21.715
.

31:25.979 --> 31:27.233
Debbie, let me ask you a question, though.

31:27.234 --> 31:30.061
On the tours you do, has anybody
ever described that to you?

31:30.062 --> 31:32.426
Oh, yeah. People all the time will say..

31:32.427 --> 31:34.506
"You know, my God, it's so
freezing cold right here,"

31:34.507 --> 31:39.127
and they'll move one foot, and it's gone.

31:41.475 --> 31:44.620
She used to travel a lot. And..

31:44.621 --> 31:47.365
She was just a nasty..

31:47.366 --> 31:48.641
Nasty lady.

31:48.642 --> 31:51.664
I don't really like her.

31:51.665 --> 31:53.705
Mackay.

31:54.073 --> 31:57.159
The woman you describe sounds
awfully like Louise Mackay,

31:57.160 --> 31:59.769
the wife of John Mackay, who
the mansion's named after.

31:59.770 --> 32:02.350
He lived here.

32:08.897 --> 32:10.344
He's an immigrant from Ireland.

32:10.345 --> 32:12.753
He came here, worked
$4 a day as a miner,

32:12.754 --> 32:15.385
and later on became one of
the richest men in America.

32:15.386 --> 32:19.499
And he married a woman named Louise.

32:19.500 --> 32:22.263
They lived here, but she
hated Virginia City.

32:22.264 --> 32:24.518
She didn't like it.
She felt she was above it.

32:24.519 --> 32:29.404
Uh, she came from a pretty
upper-class, uh, background,

32:29.405 --> 32:30.779
and the marriage wasn't really much.

32:30.780 --> 32:32.889
I mean, she spent most
of her time in Paris.

32:32.890 --> 32:36.205
Uh, so they didn't really
have a great marriage.

32:36.206 --> 32:37.707
Uh..

32:37.708 --> 32:41.147
Wh.. I see that look on your face.
What is it?

32:41.148 --> 32:45.168
Um, well, actually, I sketched her.

32:49.029 --> 32:53.899
All I remember about the sketch is that
she made me do her hair in this, like,

32:53.900 --> 32:59.468
ridiculous curly hairstyle that
took forever for the artist to do.

32:59.469 --> 33:01.247
Wh.. What did you mean, she made you?

33:01.248 --> 33:03.408
She was throwing a fit.

33:03.409 --> 33:04.334
While you were doing the sketch?

33:04.335 --> 33:06.255
Yeah.

33:26.863 --> 33:30.103
You girls look at this.

33:33.795 --> 33:36.315
(Mouths words)

33:39.242 --> 33:42.062
Not a happy lady.

33:44.547 --> 33:46.499
That's pretty good.

33:46.500 --> 33:50.040
It has the same scowl look.

33:54.645 --> 34:00.132
She's got that same look, I mean, in the
eyes, you know, just not.. Not happy.

34:00.133 --> 34:03.120
It's like a combination of both.
Hmm.

34:03.121 --> 34:06.088
And she does not like people here.

34:06.089 --> 34:07.407
Hates it.

34:07.408 --> 34:10.136
Even though she hated the place herself?

34:10.137 --> 34:10.915
Well, yeah.

34:10.916 --> 34:15.356
Anything she thought she owned, she owns.

34:15.411 --> 34:18.310
This was her space.

34:18.311 --> 34:20.935
This woman may have hated
this place in life,

34:20.936 --> 34:23.625
but I'm not surprised she
came back here in death.

34:23.626 --> 34:25.797
The dead often come back to the locations

34:25.799 --> 34:28.683
that had the most meaning in their lives.

34:28.684 --> 34:31.397
So when.. If Debbie comes in with a
tour with somebody like Valerie,

34:31.398 --> 34:32.917
I mean, she doesn't like that.

34:32.918 --> 34:34.717
No.

34:36.744 --> 34:39.094
Amy, what else did you see?

34:39.096 --> 34:40.405
A young girl.

34:40.406 --> 34:44.192
She is very ill, but she doesn't look it.

34:44.193 --> 34:46.833
And she likes..

34:47.784 --> 34:50.784
To freak people out.

34:50.980 --> 34:53.275
She likes to get on the beds..

34:53.277 --> 34:55.474
And, um, jump on things.

34:55.475 --> 34:59.195
So, yeah, she's pretty active.

35:00.425 --> 35:02.918
Debbie actually had some..

35:02.919 --> 35:04.426
What would you call it, a test?

35:04.427 --> 35:05.375
We just asked her..

35:05.376 --> 35:07.609
"Can you do something to let
us know that you're here?"

35:07.610 --> 35:10.190
And.. She did.

35:10.363 --> 35:13.294
You know, she closed the toy box lid and..

35:13.295 --> 35:16.377
Made the blanket move, and it
was like, "yeah, here I am."

35:16.378 --> 35:17.685
Wow.

35:17.686 --> 35:20.587
You saw the girl that
obviously Amy knows is here.

35:20.588 --> 35:22.094
Uh, how does that make you feel?

35:22.095 --> 35:24.924
I.. I think the way that
you explained it, Amy,

35:24.925 --> 35:30.355
when you described her, that's the
feeling that I get when I'm up there.

35:30.356 --> 35:34.321
Louise Mackay, she was a widow
whose husband had died.

35:34.322 --> 35:35.613
He was a Doctor.

35:35.614 --> 35:37.374
But they had a young girl, a daughter.

35:37.375 --> 35:38.282
Oh.

35:38.283 --> 35:41.529
And the daughter had braces on her legs.

35:41.530 --> 35:45.610
John Mackay adopted her as his own.

35:51.583 --> 35:54.572
So did you see this girl's face?

35:54.573 --> 35:57.728
No. She wouldn't let me.

35:57.729 --> 36:01.199
I hate not knowing if Mackay's
stepdaughter is this little girl,

36:01.200 --> 36:06.167
but at least I know she's not the
one terrorizing people around here.

36:06.168 --> 36:10.177
The other thing that
I saw was, uh..

36:10.178 --> 36:13.718
This really tall, dark mass.

36:13.817 --> 36:17.891
And it was definitely masculine energy.

36:17.892 --> 36:20.563
And this individual

36:20.564 --> 36:23.503
really likes to scare people.

36:23.504 --> 36:29.374
Like, to other people, he looks
very ominous and very scary.

36:29.375 --> 36:31.235
Wow.

36:32.161 --> 36:33.907
Ooh.

36:33.908 --> 36:35.828
What?

36:38.266 --> 36:41.146
Are you all right?

36:53.205 --> 36:55.697
The other thing that I saw was

36:55.698 --> 36:59.238
this really tall, dark mass.

37:00.357 --> 37:02.689
He looks very ominous.

37:02.690 --> 37:05.330
And very scary.

37:07.618 --> 37:10.498
Are you all right?

37:16.025 --> 37:18.305
Okay, so..

37:19.532 --> 37:21.410
At the tour..

37:21.411 --> 37:23.463
All of a sudden..

37:23.464 --> 37:27.484
This tall, dark, shadow man figure.

37:28.528 --> 37:32.010
Walks right between us. And..

37:32.011 --> 37:33.922
He stops.

37:33.923 --> 37:39.823
Turns around and looks straight at me
with these evil-looking, glowing eyes.

37:39.929 --> 37:42.389
And he was..

37:42.517 --> 37:44.569
So angry.

37:44.570 --> 37:47.417
I literally dropped down to my knees..

37:47.418 --> 37:50.026
And started bawling my eyes out.

37:50.027 --> 37:53.332
After that, two..
For two weeks, every single night..

37:53.333 --> 37:55.956
I had nightmares of him.

37:55.957 --> 37:59.497
I had his face in my head.

38:00.982 --> 38:03.336
Now Debby's seen this thing also.

38:03.337 --> 38:06.501
You could feel..
Feel it in the pit of your stomach.

38:06.502 --> 38:08.069
You know, his presence.

38:08.070 --> 38:10.735
And it.. It was terrifying.

38:10.736 --> 38:15.029
And it's always that feeling of dread,
the feeling of "you need to get away"

38:15.030 --> 38:19.470
"from wherever he is and away from him."

38:25.628 --> 38:28.235
Both of you have seen the
results of the investigation.

38:28.236 --> 38:30.444
And heard about Amy's walk.

38:30.445 --> 38:33.003
The reason you called us in
is because you wanna know

38:33.004 --> 38:36.649
if it's safe or not to be here or..
Or what it is.

38:36.650 --> 38:38.512
I can't answer that. Only Amy can.

38:38.513 --> 38:42.113
So, Amy, if you can, please.

38:44.564 --> 38:49.784
The man that you saw in
the yard cannot hurt you.

38:51.218 --> 38:54.818
He's just a practical joker.

38:57.730 --> 39:00.996
So I think the best way
to approach this..

39:00.997 --> 39:03.796
Is not to fall for it.

39:03.797 --> 39:07.697
Because he thinks it's hilarious.

39:08.992 --> 39:11.163
So basically..

39:11.164 --> 39:13.703
Don't feed into it and he'll..

39:13.704 --> 39:16.164
Wander about.

39:16.165 --> 39:19.755
But there are two other issues
that do need to be dealt with.

39:19.756 --> 39:22.516
And one is the..

39:22.661 --> 39:24.152
The girl.

39:24.153 --> 39:26.948
Um, she should not be here.

39:26.949 --> 39:29.949
She needs to go on.

39:30.351 --> 39:33.296
I hate seeing dead children
stuck in a location.

39:33.297 --> 39:37.551
This little girl needs to
